data.description:
FANTASTIC DEAL! Own this beautiful Beachwalk home before Christmas!

This is almost brand new 3-story house, with 3 bedrooms, 2,5 baths, screened-in lanai, and 2 car garage. Open concept layout on the main floor offers living and kitchen combo with plenty of storage space. Upstairs, you'll find three bedrooms, including a master suite with a walk-in closet, master bathroom featuring a walk-in shower, small loft, and secondary bathroom with a tub. The third floor offers a roomy loft that can serve as a guest bedroom or office. The backyard faces a tranquil preserve, providing a peaceful spot for morning coffee.
 Prime location: close to major highways, dining, shopping, A-rated schools! Amenities are 5 min away! 
The house produced steady rental income for the past year.
